Package suncertify.ui.client

Provides UI classes for client application.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ClientMainFrame Main frame for client application to view and edit contractors information.
ConnectionDialog A dialog to prompt the selection for a database file resides in file system or connecting to a database network service.
ContractorInfoPanel A panel for displaying a single contractor information.
ContractorsBookingPanel An editor for booking contractors.
ContractorsTabularViewPanel Displays a list of contractors in a tabular view.
ContractorsTabularViewPanel.ColumnConfig Defines a contractor column configuration.
RemoteConnectionInfoPanel A panel to capture configuration for remote database connection.
 

Enum Summary
ConnectionDialog.ConnectionType Defines the connection types the user can be prompted to fill its entries.
ConnectionDialog.Option Defines the option chosen by user before closing the a visible ConnectionDialog.
ContractorsTabularViewPanel.Column Define a column in contractors tabular view.
